description:
alebrijes.⌐◨-◨ is an experiment that combines Nouns and Skulls from the Alebrijes creators' Linares family.

The alebrijes.⌐◨-◨ attempt to bootstrap identity, community, and governance to decide on activities such as the selection of cities, starting February 2023, to host exhibitions of the Alebrijes, Alebrijes! collection, among others, that the community will propose. In order to spread the popular art of Mexican Cartoneria in a nounish style.
